metadata.name: Scribbling #32
metadata.description:
Let's scribble with different colors and lines...
What grids will you get?

Made with p5.js.

Keys
- 1: minimal resolution 1000x1000 (Default)
- 2: medium resolution 2000x2000
- 4: high resolution 4000x4000
- 8: super resolution 8000x8000
- s: save the image as PNG

metadata.name: Gambit #89
metadata.description:
This is an update of a project I did during Genuary 2022.
It's inspired by a background briefly shown in the tv-show "Queen's Gambit".

I added a good handful of different color palettes and some other variation.

metadata.name: Penumbra #82
metadata.description:
Penumbra is a geometric exploration of the possible outcomes from 3 basic rules:

1) Place some walls
2) Place some light sources
3) Draw the resulting shadows

This series is a small thank you to the collectors of Umbra :)
